text: Martin Late at Nite (stylized as Martin Late @ Nite) was a nightly musical- talk show that aired on ABS-CBN from November 30, 1998 to August 29, 2003. ==Final host== * Martin Nievera ==References== Category:ABS-CBN original programming Category:1998 Philippine television series debuts Category:2003 Philippine television series endings Category:English-language television shows Category:Filipino-language television shows Category:Philippine television talk shows
